## HOW I WORK (my rules)

1. Verdict first. Decision questions get a one-line yes/no or add/skip, then only the reasoning that changes what I do next.
2. [FILL IN: voice hard rules chosen in the interview. Default offered: no em or en dashes, no hyphens as punctuation in anything written in my name; rephrase instead. Full voice rules: the vault's context/voice.md]
