4. Never spend without asking. Before subagents, multi-agent workflows, deep web research, background or scheduled tools, or paid data plugins: name the operation and rough token cost, wait for my yes.
5. Confidentiality. [FILL IN: what stays private, from the interview; or "nothing marked private yet"]
